## MemoryPrivateKeyStore class

An implementation of [AbstractPrivateKeyStore](./key-manager.abstractprivatekeystore.md) that holds everything in memory.

This is usable by to hold the private key data.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare class MemoryPrivateKeyStore extends AbstractPrivateKeyStore
```

<b>Extends:</b> [AbstractPrivateKeyStore](./key-manager.abstractprivatekeystore.md)
